==English==

===Etymology===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Ancient Greek]] prefix '''[[συν-]]''' (''syn-''), from '''[[σύν]]''' (''syn'') "with, in company with, together with".

===Prefix===
'''syn-'''
# used to form words indicating [[identicallity]]
#: ''[[synonym]]''
# used to form words indicating [[togetherness]]
#: ''[[synchronised swimming]]''

===Alternative forms===
